@startuml 20-ask-citations
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Ask Citations (Mini-Cards)

actor User
participant "AskModePage" as UI
participant "POST /api/ask (SSE)" as API
participant "IChatClient" as CC
participant "Angular router" as R

... streaming tokens (flow 19) ...
CC --> API: end
API --> UI: event: citations\ndata: [c1, c2, c3]
UI -> UI: append ContactMiniCard\ninside last assistant bubble
UI --> User: 3 mini-cards visible\n(High/Mid/Low score components)
API --> UI: event: done

User -> UI: tap citation card
UI -> R: router.navigate(/contacts/:id)
R --> UI: ContactDetailPage mounts
UI --> User: contact detail loaded\n(back restores Ask view)

@enduml
